author: ekoneil
msg: Begin to support CSS class prefixes on the data grid.
This adds a simple cssNamePrefix to the datagrid tag, which is a prefix that is added to the data grid style names rendered on the header / data even and odd rows / wrapping table.

author: dolander
msg: THe FileUpload tag now reports an error when the WebApp doesn't support multipart request handling.
Changed the test webapp CoreWeb so it does support multipart request handling so the FileUpload tag can be tested.
